HEADWORD: Webby
<hw>Web"by</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Of or pertaining to a
web or webs; like a web; filled or covered with webs.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Bats on their <qex>webby</qex> wings in darkness move.</q>
<rj><qau>Crabbe.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Weber</ent>⟦br⟧
